column2: SELECT top #  s.apogee_id, a.apogee_id, a.aspcap_id,s.ra, s.dec, params.*, paramerrs.*, elemsALL.*, dbo.fApogeeAspcapFlagN(a.aspcapflag), dbo.fApogeeStarFlagN(s.starflag) into mydb.test from apogeeStar as s JOIN aspcapStar as a on a.apstar_id = s.apstar_id CROSS APPLY dbo.fAspcapParams(a.aspcap_id) params CROSS APPLY dbo.fAspcapParamErrs(a.aspcap_id) paramerrs   CROSS APPLY dbo.fAspcapElemsAll( a.aspcap_id ) elemsALL
